eesyvpn (1.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix server configuration provide by package :
    + Server configuration is now configured from template file
  * Manage embedded keys and certificates files for client configuration
  * Use easy-rsa Debian package and make-cadir tool to generate CA
  * Rework on file organization :
    + Move CA home directory in /etc/eesyvpn
    + Move some files to more logical locations
  * Fix access rigths on CA files

